Class IDiskStoreBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store.disk.IDiskStoreBuilder

  • public class IDiskStoreBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides mechanisms for building a disk-based instance-store, as represented by an IStore object.

      • addSubStore

        public void addSubStore(java.lang.String name,
                        boolean splitByFunction,
                        java.util.Collection<CIdentity> rootTypes)
        Adds a sub-component of the main instance-store, within which instances of the specified types will be stored. The sub-component can optionally be divided between IFrameFunction.ASSERTION and IFrameFunction.QUERY directories.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of sub-store, which provides name of relevant sub-directory for unified store, or base-name of sub-directories for function-split store
        splitByFunction - True if sub-store is to divided between assertion and query directories
        rootTypes - Root-types of instances to be stored in sub-store

      • addSubStore
